19namespace webrtc {
20
21absl::optional<AudioEncoderIsacFix::Config> AudioEncoderIsacFix::SdpToConfig(
22 const SdpAudioFormat& format) {
23 if (absl::EqualsIgnoreCase(format.name, "ISAC") &&
24 format.clockrate_hz == 16000 && format.num_channels == 1) {
25 Config config;
26 const auto ptime_iter = format.parameters.find("ptime");
27 if (ptime_iter != format.parameters.end()) {
28 const auto ptime = rtc::StringToNumber<int>(ptime_iter->second);
29 if (ptime && *ptime >= 60) {
30 config.frame_size_ms = 60;
31 }
32 }
33 return config;
34 } else {
35 return absl::nullopt;
36 }
37}
38
39void AudioEncoderIsacFix::AppendSupportedEncoders(
40 std::vector<AudioCodecSpec>* specs) {
41 const SdpAudioFormat fmt = {"ISAC", 16000, 1};
42 const AudioCodecInfo info = QueryAudioEncoder(*SdpToConfig(fmt));
43 specs->push_back({fmt, info});
44}
45
46AudioCodecInfo AudioEncoderIsacFix::QueryAudioEncoder(
47 AudioEncoderIsacFix::Config config) {
48 RTC_DCHECK(config.IsOk());
49 return {16000, 1, 32000, 10000, 32000};
50}
51
52std::unique_ptr<AudioEncoder> AudioEncoderIsacFix::MakeAudioEncoder(
53 AudioEncoderIsacFix::Config config,
54 int payload_type,
55 absl::optional<AudioCodecPairId> /*codec_pair_id*/) {
56 RTC_DCHECK(config.IsOk());
57 AudioEncoderIsacFixImpl::Config c;
58 c.frame_size_ms = config.frame_size_ms;
59 c.bit_rate = config.bit_rate;
60 c.payload_type = payload_type;
61 return std::make_unique<AudioEncoderIsacFixImpl>(c);
62}
